content.body:
### Shop 28L-26 Tire Size
28L-26 tires are found on both construction and agricultural equipment, and are commonly used on tractors, lawn tractors, backhoes, loaders, telehandlers, and an assortment of other machinery. These are tires that are designed with traction, stability, toughness and long service in mind, with aggressive ag or industrial tread patterns, specialty rubber formulations and reinforced, damage-resistant casings. 

Good options for 28L-26 farm tires include the Michelin CargoXbix,[Galaxy Diamond Tread R-3](https://simpletire.com/brands/galaxy-tires/diamond-tread-r-3), and Harvest King Field Pro R-3. For off-the-road (OTR) and industrial applications, take a look at the Advance LS-2 Forestry, Primex Log Monster LS2, Titan Torc-Trac Radial R-3, and [BKT Ride Max FL690 Flotation](https://simpletire.com/brands/bkt-tires/ride-max-fl-690-flotation).

Whether you need a farm, off-the-road, industrial, or another type of tire, SimpleTire has a set of 28L-26 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
